data.description: Stunning Single Family Home features 4 bedrooms, 3 full and 1 half bathrooms. Spacious Living, Dining and Family room. Full bathroom on ground floor & garage can be used as 5th bedroom, perfect for larger families. Kitchen with granite counter tops and plenty of cabinets for storage. New stainless steel appliances. Designated laundry room. Huge fully fenced backyard for security and privacy with shed for extra storage. Low HOA includes high speed fiberoptic internet, premium cable & alarm. Optional clubhouse membership available. This property is located in highly sought after "The Shores" of Keys Gate, close to Baptist hospital, shopping centers, restaurants, FL Turnpike & minutes from the FL Keys. Below Market Price Oppurtunity!!! ***SHORT SALES*** May the Force be with you!
